item.title: CVE-2023-0365|2024-08-02T05:10:55.609Z -- unknown -- react%20webcam
item.description: The React Webcam WordPress plugin through 1.2.0 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
